window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Young Torben has resigned to a mundane, sheltered existence, until a chance encounter catapults him into a world more dangerous than he ever imagined.</p> <p>In the world of Ulskandar, where humans, dwarves, and all manner of races co-exist, all must fight and die together in the wars between rival kingdoms and feral tribes. But when relics&nbsp;and powers from the past threaten to emerge, the fragile kingdoms are pushed to the brink of destruction.</p> <p>Can Torben rise to the occasion and become the hero the realm needs, or will he fall like so many others before him?</p>"; 
